    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It works for your current usecase but this would be a hack and ultimately is trying to make part of the full template feature inside the API by adding ˋlabel`.\n\nIt does not answer @Jerskouille usecase who wants to completely hide the panel when no results.\n\nNot very extensive, what about panel footer, wrapper etc.. What about I want to keep the panel but grayed when no refinements available?\n\nLabel would be a cool shortcut for our current magento need ok but do not looks like a solution to our templating limitations.\n\nThose api changes will come again and again and are already crippling the api (root class, item class, now label then id and ..). All rooting to a templating limitation\n\nLets fix that instead?\n",
